verbose_text: In a study that specifically looked at the regulation of AR signaling by resveratrol, it was observed that treatment with 10 muM resveratrol for just 3 h inhibited the acetylation of AR and affected the binding of AR to the enhancer region of prostate specific antigen (PSA) [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: resveratrol for just 3 h inhibited the acetylation of AR
